
                          VCloud Automation Deployment Tool
                          --------------------------------

  What is it?
  -----------

  This is an automation tool to deploy VAPP's and VM's on the VCloud platform. It directly queries the VCLoud library to deploy VAPPs and VM.


  The Latest Version
  ------------------

  Details of the latest version can be found on the Github
  vCloud automation project page under https://github.com/krisdigitx/python-vcloud-automation

  Documentation
  -------------

  Refer to the README file included in the repository and the VCloud API Programming Guide
  http://pubs.vmware.com/vcd-51/index.jsp?topic=%2Fcom.vmware.vcloud.api.reference.doc_51%2Fdoc%2Findex.html


  Installation
  ------------

  python setup.py install


  Usage
  ---------
  The installation will deploy the tool in /usr/local/bin/vcloud, a sample VAPP configuration file is included under
  vcloud-automation/config/vcloud.ini

  Run the tool with the vapp configuration file using

  vcloud -c vcloud.ini


